George Chesebro https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Chesebro 0 George Chesebro (July 29, 1888 – May 28, 1959) was an American film actor. He appeared in more than 400 films between 1915 and 1954, beginning in two reelers starring Texas Guinan. He was born in Minneapolis, Minnesota and died in Los Angeles, California.
